name: randomelement
0:
”Alexa, launch random element.”
”Alexa, open random element.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: random element
des:
You can create a list of elements and then choose a random element until your list is empty.
If you want to add an element to your list, say ADD or NEW ELEMENT followed by "your element".
If you want to choose an element from your list, say CHOOSE.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
